{"type":"message","id":"c53d0c73","parentId":"b560b413","timestamp":"2026-04-09T11:26:45.502Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"目录创建好了，用户想让我开发一个全栈项目，包含：\n1. 前端 - Web界面\n2. 后端 - API服务\n3. 音频分析 - 猫叫声分类\n4. 图像分析 - 猫表情/状态识别\n5. 心情判断 - 综合判断\n\n我需要写一个技术方案，然后开始实现。但用户说\"先评分，全部由你自己来\"，意思应该是让我自己决定怎么做，不需要再问用户。\n\n让我开始写项目结构和代码。由于复杂，我需要分步骤：\n\n1. 先写 SPEC.md (技术规格)\n2. 后端 - FastAPI + 音频/图像分析\n3. 前端 - 简洁的HTML页面\n4. 运行验证\n\n让我开始。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d71fdae87e91df1284be43dc1fb87","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# CatMood - 小猫心情识别系统\n\n## 项目概述\n\n通过分析猫的叫声和图片，判断猫的心情。\n\n## 技术栈\n\n| 层级 | 技术 |\n|------|------|\n| 后端 | Python FastAPI |\n| 音频分析 | librosa 特征提取 + 随机森林分类 |\n| 图像分析 | OpenCV + CNN 表情分析 |\n| 前端 | 原生 HTML/CSS/JS |\n\n## API 设计\n\n```\nPOST /api/analyze\n  - form-data: audio(文件), image(文件)\n  - return: { mood: string, confidence: float, details: {...} }\n```\n\n## 心情分类\n\n- 😺 开心 (happy)\n- 😾 生气 (angry)  \n- 😻 放松 (relaxed)\n- 😿 紧张/害怕 (nervous)\n- 😴 困倦 (sleepy)\n- 🐱 警觉 (alert)\n\n## 模块说明\n\n1. **audio_analyzer.py** - 叫声特征提取与分类\n2. **image_analyzer.py** - 图像姿态/表情分析\n3. **mood_judge.py** - 综合判断逻辑\n4. **main.py** - FastAPI 服务入口\n5. **static/** - 前端页面","path":"/home/ai/projects/cat-mood/SPEC.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":452,"output":459,"cacheRead":18816,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19727,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775733958403,"responseId":"019d71fd5178f4d989c79e8c8c44bc48"}}
