{"type":"message","id":"2cc17248","parentId":"92d18d7b","timestamp":"2026-04-09T11:35:30.042Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这是控制界面，不是任务编排器 API。让我看看实际的子代理执行方案。既然用户要求最高规格，我应该 spawn 一个 subagent 来执行完整的全栈项目开发。\n\n按照 AGENTS.md 的指导，这应该用 SPAWN_SUBAGENT 或 MEGA_TASK。让我用一个专门的子代理来完整开发这个项目。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_422a0abe498b4c7eb7f5d97e","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"开发一个完整的猫心情识别全栈项目：\n\n## 项目目录\n/home/ai/projects/cat-mood\n\n## 技术栈\n- 后端：Python FastAPI\n- 音频分析：librosa 特征提取 + 机器学习分类\n- 图像分析：OpenCV + 视觉模型\n- 前端：现代 Web 界面\n\n## 功能要求\n1. 用户上传猫叫声音频和图片\n2. 后端分析叫声类型（喵叫/咕噜/嘶嘶等）\n3. 后端分析图片中的猫表情和姿态\n4. 综合判断猫的心情（开心/生气/放松/紧张/困倦/警觉）\n5. 返回心情结果和置信度\n\n## 文件结构\n- backend/main.py - FastAPI 服务\n- backend/audio_analyzer.py - 音频分析模块\n- backend/image_analyzer.py - 图像分析模块  \n- backend/mood_judge.py - 心情判断逻辑\n- frontend/index.html - 上传和分析界面\n- requirements.txt - 依赖\n- SPEC.md - 规格文档\n\n## 输出\n完成后启动服务，验证前后端正常工作。","label":"cat-mood-fullstack","runtime":"subagent","runTimeoutSeconds":7200}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":20782,"output":360,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21142,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775734524836,"responseId":"chatcmpl-705cf4b0-4642-4473-b3ee-a9c3ff93f2dc"}}
