{"type":"message","id":"890ca49f","parentId":"99fed396","timestamp":"2026-04-09T11:45:08.129Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"子代理完成了CatMood全栈项目的开发。现在需要向用户汇报结果。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## CatMood 项目开发完成 ✅\n\n已创建完整的小猫心情识别全栈项目：\n\n### 项目结构\n```\n/home/ai/projects/cat-mood/\n├── backend/\n│   ├── main.py          # FastAPI 服务\n│   ├── audio_analyzer.py # 音频分析（叫声分类）\n│   ├── image_analyzer.py # 图像分析（表情识别）\n│   └── mood_judge.py    # 心情综合判断\n├── frontend/\n│   └── index.html       # Web 上传界面\n├── requirements.txt\n└── SPEC.md\n```\n\n### 服务状态\n| 地址 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| http://localhost:8000/ui | 前端界面 |\n| http://localhost:8000/analyze | 分析 API |\n\n### 功能\n- 上传猫叫声音频 → 识别叫声类型（喵叫/咕噜/嘶嘶/咆哮）\n- 上传猫照片 → 识别表情（放松/紧张/生气/开心/困倦/警觉）\n- 综合判断最终心情和置信度\n\n可以打开 `http://localhost:8000/ui` 体验了。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":18411,"output":248,"cacheRead":384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19043,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775735092203,"responseId":"019d720e6b7ef3d328acc6f6f3872134"}}
